<p>
	For this week&#39;s episode, John and Dave are here again to answer your questions and share their tips. Some key topics covered include solving a pesky MacBook Pro lockup, configuring your own (free!) VPN server, some tips for Touch ID users and configuring your own email domain so you&#39;ll never have to worry when changing ISPs again! Download today for free and enjoy!</p>
